Goals:
    - implement an MVC architecture

Model:
    - manage underlying data type <Book>
    - manage access to files
    - communicates only with controller

View:
    - mainwindow should be clear of any references to underlying data type < Book >
    - should communicate only with controller

Controller:
    - manage communication between view and model
    - manage app threads
    - conversion between model data type and view data type
    - informs view to change it's state

